Full description
This is a PHP based forum that includes the following basic functionality:
•	Registration
•	Login
•	Recover password
•	Change password
•	Create category(admin)
•	Edit category(admin)
•	Delete categories(admin)
•	Post threads
- Post replies

Functionality that may be added in future.
•	Mentioning system
•	Private messaging 
•	Avatar
•	Chatbox
•	Status update

How to guide.
1.	Open connection_to_db.php file and write down your dataabse details, hostname, username, password and databse name.
2.	Change site_name name in form_registration_class.php on line 110 to your website/forum link, and "from" to your website's name, for example "sam forums".
There is no need to import database or table, I have written all the queries, that should make required tables for you

